        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Yes I was aware of (some of) the context but added the ts label to gather feedback on potentially using a string parser for ui2, thanks. I think it makes sense/is necessary as seen in the improved highlighting for the affected block mode tests. As long as it doesn't clash with whats planned for vim.treesitter I would think it's a welcome improvement.",
