            "body": "Yup, just wanted to link the discussion for documentation purposes. A custom \"lightweight\" highlighter for the command line makes more sense than a persistent buffer highlighter. And I think the strategy (as mentioned in the issue) aligns with that as well (modulo injection handling).",
